# Restaurant UI (UI UX Pro Max)

When editing UI, styling, or layout:

1. Read `design-system/restaurante-progra/MASTER.md` (and page overrides in `design-system/restaurante-progra/pages/` if present).
2. Follow `.cursor/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/SKILL.md` workflow for new screens.
3. Regenerate design hints when the product changes:
   ```bash
   python .cursor/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/scripts/search.py "<query>" --design-system --persist -p "Restaurante Progra" --stack react
   ```

## Stack rules

- React 19 + Tailwind v4 + Lucide icons (no emoji icons).
- Use shell primitives: `AppButton`, `AppIconButton`, `AppLink`, `panelClass`, `inputClass`, `selectClass`, `app-table`.
- Primary CTA = gold (`--color-cta`), headings = Playfair Display SC, body = Karla.
- All clickables: `cursor-pointer`, transitions 150–300ms, visible focus rings.
- Keep `api/` free of presentation logic.
